                <div class="kicker"><span class="kicker"><a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/news">NEWS</a></span></div>

                <h1>The Construction Obstruction</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/6bca6898-e1a7-4ad9-8fd7-6cc2bb23ef78.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="The&#x20;closure&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;main&#x20;entrance&#x20;to&#x20;Perkins&#x20;Library&#x20;is&#x20;just&#x20;part&#x20;of&#x20;a&#x20;slew&#x20;of&#x20;projects&#x20;sweeping&#x20;across&#x20;Duke&#x27;s&#x20;West&#x20;Campus." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            The closure of the main entrance to Perkins Library is just part of a slew of projects sweeping across Duke's West Campus.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
